[section#multibyte.strings
    [:en] Multibyte strings
    [:zh_CN] 多字节字符串
]

[para]
[:en]
A [%NTBS] [%NTMBS] [%string[!null-terminated multibyte]] [+null-terminated
multibyte string,] or [em@sc ntmbs], is an [em@sc ntbs] that constitutes a
sequence of valid multibyte characters, beginning and ending in the initial
shift state.
[:zh_CN]
[%NTBS] [%NTMBS] [%字符串[!空终结多字节～]] [+空终结多字节字符串]，或
[em@sc ntmbs]，是由有效的，开始并结束于初始转移状态的多字节字符的序列所构成的
[em@sc ntbs]。

[footnote]
[:en]
An [em@sc ntbs] that contains characters only from the basic execution character
set is also an [em@sc ntmbs].
[:zh_CN]
仅包含基本执行字符集中的字符的 [em@sc ntbs] 也是 [em@sc ntmbs]。

[:en]
Each multibyte character then consists of a single byte.
[:zh_CN]
此时每个多字节字符由单个字节构成。
[footnote:end]

[para]
[:en]
[%NTMBS[!static]] [%NTMBS]
A [+static] [em@sc ntmbs] is an [em@sc ntmbs] with static storage duration.
[:zh_CN]
[%NTMBS[!静态～]] [%NTMBS]
[+静态] [em@sc ntmbs] 为具有静态存储期的 [em@sc ntmbs]。
